#

Lemon-Infused Pork Parmesan

$25
800 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

DairyPork

Dietary Tags:

High-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodGourmet

Description

A zesty twist on classic parmesan, featuring tender pork cutlets infused with lemon and topped with a rich, hearty tomato ragu.

Ingredients

  • Pork Cutlets: 4 pieces
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Fresh Mozzarella: 1 cup, sliced
  • Tomato Sauce: 2 cups
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Lemon Zest: 1 tablespoon
  • Fresh Basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
